flowchart LR
  A[Agent Runtime
  (e.g., Claude Code)] -->|MCP request| G[MCP Context Gateway
  (compress + store raw)]
  G -->|MCP request| T[Tool / MCP Server]
  T -->|Raw output (large)| G

  G -->|Store raw| B[(Blob Store / Cache)]
